  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e        \u003cdiv\u003e\n        \u003ch3\u003eQuick Links\u003c/h3\u003e\n        \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                                                                                    \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                        \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"#why-is-google-chrome-not-opening-on-children-39-s-accounts\"\u003eWhy Is Google Chrome Not Opening on Children\u0026#39;s Accounts?\u003c/a\u003e\n                                        \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n                                                                                            \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                        \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"#unblock-chrome-from-family-safety-settings\"\u003eUnblock Chrome from Family Safety Settings\u003c/a\u003e\n                                        \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n                                                                                            \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                        \u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"#enable-the-activity-reporting-feature\"\u003eEnable the Activity Reporting Feature\u003c/a\u003e\n                                        \u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n                                    \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n                                                                                            \u003cul\u003e\n                \u003cli\u003e\n                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                   